萬，上千萬，但難道你們就只管那些人的死活，不管我們的死活了嗎？雖然我知道內地和香港是兩個法治體系，連國情都不一樣，但是兩邊的警察同樣讓我失望。」...&quot;<br />\n<br />\n真係天真過天真嬌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50caf2ba9b4dc1bc02071654bf7e621e3f15de9d","tid":1089989,"uid":128417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T07:46:11.000Z","msg":"讀緊大學 但個腦仲係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw 究竟香港堆大學收左幾多大陸人<br />\n班友住夠7年自動變腥港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a4644f8426646fb8ac3681b385dcc0ed9fb129f","tid":1089989,"uid":55924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T07:49:10.000Z","msg":"但微信收款完全唔經香港都拉到咩"},{"pid":"77d55c623799a353dd4232030acda2bc7454776c","tid":1089989,"uid":61280,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T07:50:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />高分低能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">低能嘅好可能係妓者，左膠同你囉！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幾個電話就抬幾十甚至幾百個？？你落街搵港西請你飲杯Starbucks睇下十隻有冇1隻？？？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n洗錢就洗錢啦仆街！！！</span></span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4beadd6984a485aa471ab1c30ea3a2c4fc1d5117","tid":1089989,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T07:51:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/h